text: Baicha or bai cha may refer to: *White tea, several styles of tea using young or minimally-processed tea leaves *Anji bai cha, grean tea variety produced in Anji, Zhejiang, China *Baicha, Jiangxi, town in Yongxiu County, Jiujiang, Jiangxi, China *Bai cha, a Khmer variation of fried rice
title: Baicha
